data.description: Excellent 2021 CAVCO on 3.63 Acres!  Top of the line home, the great room is perfect for gatherings, wonderful kitchen and the master bathroom is truly luxurious. With 9 ft ceilings and R42 insulation, this home is designed for comfort and efficiency.  Numerous upgrades ensure that this property stands out.  The saltwater above-ground pool & deck and a relaxing hot tub are a plus.   Automatic entry gate for easy entry and the entire area is securely fenced, no climb fencing.  There's even a double metal shed with a concrete floor, featuring electricity and two workbenches. This property is a rare find as it's not governed by an HOA and is nestled in the awe-inspiring natural beauty of the southwest. Enjoy peace, privacy, and breathtaking mountain views. 50 AMP RV HU.
